{"tid":1603610,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲全民練武練跑 依家打緊仗","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T00:11:38.000Z","uid":285790,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe3f4d6e81fde117d5b72a1bd495b7f92a1720b","tid":1603610,"uid":285790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"日日睇住前線俾popo扑到頭破血流<br />\n救得翻既手足又唔多<br />\n以下係正確示範<br />\n拯救被警渣包圍既女仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gc9XHDF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgc9XHDF.jpg&h=a58bc960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之全民練武，巴西柔術、拳擊、合氣道，泰拳etc<br />\n唔練武都同我練跑打好個底<br />\n救唔到手足都要自己跑得甩<br />\n<br />\n身體差既跑唔到又練唔到武<br />\n都去讀下兵法書戰術書歷史書<br />\n今日popo擺明用左戰術<br />\n未出發就先出彈挑起民憤<br />\n又用直升機高處偵測示威者分佈<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以再失去手足了"},{"pid":"c824e9d1aa3b76d21679211c610d8d7a9946ea48","tid":1603610,"uid":148824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:59:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n菲律賓魔棍 長棍 上網有影片教學"},{"pid":"458b89a124c7db980bb48d5e744f67f23c5a91b4","tid":1603610,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:00:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"23f483a85fe2b58a4ebcc24b5133edee5b4d6634","tid":1603610,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:04:29.000Z","msg":"屌好型呀"},{"pid":"f2a1532ad7b2800c07a26b0e1b3ac07ce2967525","tid":1603610,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"拉打kick"},{"pid":"c08af6545d096bff0912e97aec7b9a694fb83aee","tid":1603610,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:10:14.000Z","msg":"有冇簡單易學快上手"},{"pid":"3803b2cef08217ad87946f0319e7edfcde5e5ab9","tid":1603610,"uid":18688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c08af6545d096bff0912e97aec7b9a694fb83aee","tid":1603610,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:10:14.000Z","msg":"有冇簡單